e:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体;color:black\">（T+2）</span></p></td><td width=\"440\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 1px 1px 0px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:13px;margin-bottom:   5px;margin-left:0;text-indent:27px;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">本产品在申购开放日后<span style=\"color:black\">第二个交易日（T+2日）</span>对申购申请的有效性进行确认。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:13px;margin-bottom:   5px;margin-left:0;text-indent:27px;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">申购遵循“未知价”原则，申购资金按开放日产品份额净值折算份额。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:27px;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">申购份额=申购金额÷开放日产品份额净值。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:27px;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体\">投资者多笔申购本产品时，按照上述公式逐笔计算申购份额后加总。</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\";height:30px\"><td width=\"132\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 1px 1px 0px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体;color:black\">产品赎回及确认</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:110%\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:110%;font-family:宋体;color:black\">(T+2)</span></p></td><td width=\"440\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 1px 1px 0px;\" height=\"30\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:13px;margin-bottom:   